<H3> <TI>   Bauman Institute to Receive State Scientific Center Status </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bauman Institute to Receive State Scientific Center Status </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   947A0033B Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI in Russian 1 Mar 94 p 8 </F>
<F P=103> 947A0033B </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI </F>
