               Leaves         0.11              0.51           - 





  Table 4. The [.sup]90[/]Sr and [.sup]134+137[/]Cs Content in the Soil of Forest Stands 
Within the 30-Kilometer Zone of the CNPS Accident, kBq/m[.sup]2[/] 

Section      Year    [.sup]90[/]Sr    [.sup]134+137[/]Cs    [.sup] 90[/]Sr/[.sup]134+137[/]Cs 

